Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:31.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:37.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任憑此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握緊冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:48.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}臉上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有視野漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:57.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言語粉飾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:00.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}有始必定有終
