Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防護罩消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人前進方向未變 正在直奔這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直衝過來嗎 真夠猖狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我申請過外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣 有些人現在體力衰弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候還窩裡鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴嗎？你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件事要拜託把我裝進系統的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是生平第一次到外面來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以還不太會走路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 帶上能帶著我一起移動的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2重力波防護罩被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校也挺有鬥志的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也比平時要精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 因為去見了見過去的女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 神劍型出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人從西南沿岸登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們自爆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普勒阿得斯型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.85,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,1000)}Pleiades
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.85,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：希臘神話中提坦神阿特拉斯和大洋神女普勒俄涅所生的七個女兒的統稱 代表天上的昴星團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,666 過去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 讓第3部隊繞到左邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來個兩面夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的 連無線都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 Mk.Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺機體的表面就像自己的皮膚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然會變得這麼大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體好重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是神劍型的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和機體融為一體 接受意識改變狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳 站起來戰鬥 找死嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣和你對話還是第一次呢 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒蛇級菲馬艦遭到直擊 三艘全都被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.61,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(276,1000)}Serpent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.61,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,1000)}Firma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的老大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知剩下兩艘 對西南部沿岸進行飽和攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 連自己人都打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生來第一次玩泥巴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 只是燒著了表面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才要真正做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西面出現第三群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分離島的西南部 命令系統自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把登陸的敵人邊同島一起炸飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎擊系統自動運作 控制命令被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在操作！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門鎖打開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飯點到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總部 總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子指揮系統斷裂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形勢已變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我要過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰在控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是那邊放下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子是想把我們引到什麼地方去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重建防線！能動的人上前來！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量普勒阿得斯型聚集在龍宮山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡的正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 只是島的疼痛傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是有個三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算繼續躲下去 島也只會沉沒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在那之前讓大家選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞要區域…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏爾德之泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是被強加的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要憑自己的意願重新選擇是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別杵著了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒換戰鬥服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎也穿著平時的衣服直接開過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要是不戰鬥 就太對不起爸爸和甲洋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的使命是給予大家他們所追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓他們重新選擇一次 那是不是他們真正想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要讓他們自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為此才出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩體還是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪我到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為系統的研究員…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為生活在島上的一員 我想見證這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子 你也到這來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我是被引過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是亞瑟之室…第二CDC嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:19.37,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,1000)}Arthur's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的基本構造和CDC一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有系統已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備奪回島的控制權
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們想要如何對待島 是他們的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:13:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓他們知道自己真正的追求是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有讓他們自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓他們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒能讓你有所選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前登陸個體117隻 敵軍數量繼續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普勒阿得斯型發現這裡只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二防禦系統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在訪問 兩分鐘後完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敵對生出敵群的本體無效 找不到牠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用法芙娜當誘餌把敵人的首領引出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太容易 不過我會試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門發出應答 是敵人的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓所有迎擊系統對準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌聲是從哪裡傳來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島西部燈塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在顯示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連祝福者你也要給牠選擇的機會嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人本體開始朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜全機散開並火速趕往西面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲過敵群 於指定地點集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要擊潰敵人的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒你們 無論是什麼樣的敵人我都要打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種動作…駕駛員換人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 找到敵人的老大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到西邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還能動的傢伙也跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦飛彈 訪問完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.37,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(604,1000)}denial
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅴ用埃癸斯護盾擋住敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅷ繞到右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅲ去確認敵人的內核並將之破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過去 維持隊形！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁 沒趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連神劍型也對付不了牠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘖 該死的怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標再次向燈塔前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城乙姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你們也選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有對話的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都消失不見的虛無之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出選擇的並不只有你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擋住了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是剛才的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 會被消滅的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的內核…正在自內而外消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是把祝福者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向同化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標再次開始消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要去找就能找到的 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振動 各類波形 溫度 電子 電波 空間位相…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部機體攻擊牠時造成的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經捕捉到敵人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把牠打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一…騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和系統同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該和Mk.Ⅺ一樣 是可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 你還要做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你曾說過只有這個島是樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我不知道這句話的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是照著你說的去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在 我感覺我有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在承受著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我們還什麼都不知道的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在努力保護著島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子那時 甲洋那時 你都一個人承受著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部機體的識別代碼是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要登記機體以便跟你同步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登記完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:14.57,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,1000)}enroll
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始同步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 看得到我看的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那武器是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是Mk.Ⅷ的加姆44
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.02,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(872,1000)}Garm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.02,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：法芙娜用的來復槍 名稱取自北歐神話中的地獄犬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是雷擊槍嗎
